bilingual.source: They strive for excellence in their work.
bilingual.target: 他们在工作中努力追求卓越。

bilingual.source: He pursues excellence in everything he does.
bilingual.target: 他在做每件事时都追求卓越。

bilingual.source: The restaurant is known for its culinary excellence.
bilingual.target: 这家餐厅以其烹饪卓越而闻名。

bilingual.source: The school is known for its excellence in education.
bilingual.target: 这所学校以其教育卓越而闻名。

bilingual.source: Striving for excellence means not accepting mediocrity.
bilingual.target: 追求卓越意味着不接受平庸。

bilingual.source: She strives for excellence in everything she does.
bilingual.target: 她在做的每一件事中都追求卓越。

bilingual.source: Daks has a long history of fashion excellence.
bilingual.target: 达克斯在时尚界有着悠久的卓越历史。

bilingual.source: The teacher described him as a paragon of academic excellence.
bilingual.target: 老师称他为学术卓越的典范。

bilingual.source: She achieved supre excellence in her field of study.
bilingual.target: 她在她的研究领域达到了最高的卓越。

bilingual.source: His unremitting pursuit of excellence is truly inspiring.
bilingual.target: 他对卓越的不懈的追求确实令人鼓舞。

list.abstract: excellence，英语单词，主要用作为名词，用作名词译为“优点优秀，卓越;美德”。

yingyinNormal.en: Runway and James Holt share many things in common, chief among them, a commitment to excellence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 《天桥》与詹姆斯·浩特，有着许多的共同之处，最重要的是，都拥有对达到完美卓越的渴望。

yingyinNormal.en: Many years since I've had such an exemplary vegetable. To which my fair cousin should I compliment the excellence of the cooking?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我好多年都没有吃到这样的蔬菜了。这些佳肴是哪位表妹烹调的？

yingyinNormal.en: How can I describe it? Good food is like music you can taste, color you can smell. There is excellence all around you. You need only be aware to stop and savor it. Oh, Gusteau was right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 该怎么形容呢? 美食就像可口的音乐，闻得到的色彩，你的身边处处皆美食，你只须留心并伫足品尝。食神说得对。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
